          <heading>Section 388-52</heading>
          <content>
            <p>§388-52
Penalties
.  Any employer
found in violation of section 388-51 shall be subject to a fine of no less than
$250 nor more than $2,500 to be collected by the director and the fine shall
not be suspended.  Each violation shall constitute a separate offense.  Amounts
so collected by the director shall be paid into the general fund. [L 1987, c
169, §2; am L 2020, c 44, §12]
